    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 60,
      "text": "Gentlemen: Flying Discs",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 61,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 62,
      "text": "I qualify myself as a layman, and amateur scientist",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 63,
      "text": "in my own fields who has read your public documents,",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 64,
      "text": "\"Nuclear Rocket Propulsion,\" etc. I am also a person wh",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 65,
      "text": "has seen several unidentified flying objects. One of in",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 66,
      "text": "saucer shape performed certain feats at incredible speed",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 67,
      "text": "far beyond the power of any propulsion system which we",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68,
      "text": "currently use. I am also familiar with the reported",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 69,
      "text": "sightings of such craft for many centuries and in variou",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70,
      "text": "places. I am also aware that the connecting link betwee",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 71,
      "text": "energy and matter, the proton nucleus of hydrogen, was",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 72,
      "text": "probably created by the electro-magnetic fusion of radio",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 73,
      "text": "gallaxies in an original electron atmosphere. Quite",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 74,
      "text": "naturally I have at various times researched pertinent",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 75,
      "text": "subjects in an attempt to figure out how such interstell",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 76,
      "text": "space craft operate. Perhaps I'm like a lot of others w",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 77,
      "text": "can't see the forest because of the trees. Yet I may ha",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 78,
      "text": "hit upon a workable system capable of being created with",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 79,
      "text": "our present technology, materials and methods. In the",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 80,
      "text": "interest of the United States first, I pass these on to",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 81,
      "text": "They are embodied in a treatise upon which I am working",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 82,
      "text": "titled \"The Worlds And You In The Making.\" I quote:",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 83,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
