      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 88,
      "text": "intakes and suction compressors into a liquid hydrogen f",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89,
      "text": "tank? That from this continually unlimited fuel reserve",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 90,
      "text": "second stage compressors convert the hydrogen into an",
