    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 91,
      "text": "expanding gas fed into a second semi-ready heater tank,",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 92,
      "text": "compressors upon each end to force the semi-ready fuel f",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 93,
      "text": "from the tank's center. And into a \"pod\" of four therma",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 94,
      "text": "reactors angled to fire to a central point behind outsid",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
